About Me

I am currently a final-year PhD student in School of Data Science at Fudan University, under the advised of Prof.Xuening Zhu. I obtained my Bachelors Degree in Economics and Masters Degree in Applied Statistics from School of Statistics at Renmin University of China. My research interest lies in Network Analysis, High-dimensional Statistics, Spatial Econometrics, and Statistical Machine Learning.
